result.name: Identification and annotation of human genetic variants on primary cells obtained from nasal brushing
result.description: Variants were identified and annotated by analyzing reads arising from a whole exome sequencing (WES), performed on human primary cells obtained from nasal brushing from a male healthy subject
result.center: CEINGE Biotecnologie Avanzate; Dipartimento di Medicina molecolare e Biotecnologie Mediche DMMBM University of Naples, Federico II
